499
00:32:33,608 --> 00:32:37,101
I have no idea what was in it, but I'm
positive it wouldn't get FDA approval.

500
00:32:37,207 --> 00:32:41,701
It tasted just you know, pine tar
and a little hint of bat urine.

501
00:32:41,805 --> 00:32:43,302
Oh, that's nice. That's romantic.

502
00:32:43,407 --> 00:32:44,903
Actually, it was.

503
00:32:45,007 --> 00:32:46,903
I had...

504
00:32:47,008 --> 00:32:52,602
I had the most incredible visions,
all of them involving you.

505
00:32:52,705 --> 00:32:56,803
And they swore to me
that it would increase sexual...

506
00:32:56,907 --> 00:32:59,200
Ok, ok, ok. Fine, fine.

507
00:32:59,308 --> 00:33:02,300
So when do we go?

508
00:33:03,105 --> 00:33:05,501
3 hours.

509
00:33:05,607 --> 00:33:08,602
And apparently it's quite a hike.

510
00:33:08,708 --> 00:33:12,500
- Is that ok with you?
- Yeah.

511
00:33:13,805 --> 00:33:15,900
You're a little hot.
Do you feel ok?

512
00:33:16,008 --> 00:33:20,103
Oh, yeah. If I'm hot,
it's just because I'm here with you.

513
00:33:20,207 --> 00:33:22,600
- I'm telling you, those visions...
