524
00:33:49,107 --> 00:33:51,403
Call.

525
00:33:59,505 --> 00:34:01,902
Sorry!

526
00:34:24,807 --> 00:34:26,003
How's dr. Grogan?

527
00:34:26,106 --> 00:34:28,000
We got in there just in time.

528
00:34:28,105 --> 00:34:32,703
They pumped her stomach immediately,
