529
00:34:32,807 --> 00:34:35,503
You saved her life, you know.

530
00:34:35,608 --> 00:34:38,600
You know, people get awards from
the mayor for doing that sort of thing.

531
00:34:38,705 --> 00:34:42,500
I'd have to share mine with a ghost.
He told me.

532
00:34:42,607 --> 00:34:46,801
Tell me, what was
